 1999-19181999-10-260,  ,  ,  INDUSTRY, 
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Industry of SPYRO TRIFOS, of Sydney, Nova Scotia, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Enterprise Cape Breton Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of two years, in the place of Charles T. Smith, whose term has expired.
